Technology Co. said its unit Beijing Tianrun New Energy
Investment Co. will sell a 49 percent stake in Damaoqi Tianrun
Wind Power Co. for 209.3 million yuan ($31 million).  The buyer is China Ping An Trust & Investment Co., a unit
of Ping An Insurance Group Co. of China, Goldwind said today in
